-06-28-Spring-vs-SpringBoot/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/ETC/2022-06-27-Framework-vs-Library/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Framework vs Library (feat. IoC, 왜 프레임워크를 써야할까?)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Spring/2022-06-29-ArgumentResolver란/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Spring] ArgumentResolver란 무엇일까?"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3911196313","4111100897"]}